}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The [[EcoNet]] EN7526GT CPU (as labeled in the [https://fccid.io/2ADZRG240WFV2/Internal-Photos/Internal-photos-3613425 FCC photos]) may be a [[MediaTek]] :MTK7526G (seen in a screenshot of the Web interface in the User Manual). The 2.4GHz radio is probably 2x2:2, but FCC documents only say "MIMO".
:''See also: [http://koolshare.cn/thread-122677-1-1.html Bell] [http://koolshare.cn/thread-121156-1-1.html '''G-140W-C'''] ([[Gemtek]]) and [http://bbs.mydigit.cn/read.php?tid=2193315&page=4 HG6821M] ([[MitraStar]])''
